32
00:01:25,450 --> 00:01:28,850
<font face="Serif" size="18">Old Man Hansen, do you sell
Bazooka Sharks merchandise?</font>

33
00:01:28,850 --> 00:01:31,620
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm looking for one of those
Snuggies with a built-in diaper</font>

34
00:01:31,620 --> 00:01:33,250
<font face="Serif" size="18">and a place I can put
 my driver's license.</font>

35
00:01:33,260 --> 00:01:35,790
<font face="Serif" size="18">That blasted
            arena football team!</font>

36
00:01:35,790 --> 00:01:38,390
<font face="Serif" size="18">We've been here
              three generations,</font>

37
00:01:38,390 --> 00:01:41,530
<font face="Serif" size="18">and now they're tearing us down
    to put in the new stadium.</font>

38
00:01:41,530 --> 00:01:44,230
<font face="Serif" size="18">You poor old man.</font>

39
00:01:44,230 --> 00:01:46,700
<font face="Serif" size="18">This lamp sucks.
   I'll give you 2 bucks for it.</font>

40
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:48,770
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mom!
 That is disgusting.</font>

41
00:01:48,770 --> 00:01:51,110
<font face="Serif" size="18">Taking advantage of -- Wait.
     Half off this bird cage?</font>

42
00:01:51,110 --> 00:01:53,370
<font face="Serif" size="18">Please,
I could really use this.</font>

43
00:01:53,380 --> 00:01:55,640
<font face="Serif" size="18">I foster abused birds.</font>

44
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,880
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'd like to
