45
00:01:57,880 --> 00:02:00,210
<font face="Serif" size="18">I still have one shot
             to save the store.</font>

46
00:02:00,220 --> 00:02:03,380
<font face="Serif" size="18">There's a town council meeting
    about the stadium tonight.</font>

47
00:02:03,390 --> 00:02:06,150
<font face="Serif" size="18">Tonight, eh?
  Oh, I'll be there.</font>

48
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:09,320
<font face="Serif" size="18">Please don't come if you're
      gonna support the stadium.</font>

49
00:02:09,330 --> 00:02:11,960
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's too late.</font>

50
00:02:15,130 --> 00:02:17,830
<font face="Serif" size="18">What's to become of you with
   the store closing, Petruchio?</font>

51
00:02:17,830 --> 00:02:20,830
<font face="Serif" size="18">It could-a be time to find
  the guy who killed my brother.</font>

52
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,770
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mm, now,
 what is this lining?</font>

53
00:02:22,770 --> 00:02:25,410
<font face="Serif" size="18">Is a fine Bemberg lining,
               Mr. Steve.</font>

54
00:02:25,410 --> 00:02:27,640
<font face="Serif" size="18">Bemberg, not silk.</font>

55
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:30,480
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, you've been right about
this kind of thing before.</font>

56
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:32,850
<font face="Serif" size="18">Snot went nuts for me
     in paisley.</font>

57
00:02:32,850 --> 00:02:35,320
<font face="Serif" size="18">Inseam always-a 20 inches.</font>

58
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:37,320
<font face="Serif" size="18">I-Is that unusual?</font>

59
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:40,450
<font face="Serif" size="18">You see, all the other boys --
          bum, bum, bum,</font>

60
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:41,920
<font face="Serif" size="18">they are growing.</font>

61
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:45,760
<font face="Serif" size="18">You -- bum, bum, bum.
        You hear the difference?</font>

62
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:48,300
<font face="Serif" size="18">They go on
          to men's-a department.</font>

63
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:51,200
<font face="Serif" size="18">But you stay
               with Petruchio.</font>

64
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:53,970
<font face="Serif" size="18">Y-You're telling me
         I'm not growing at all?</font>

65
00:02:53,970 --> 00:02:55,840
<font face="Serif" size="18">Not in two years.</font>

66
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:58,940
<font face="Serif" size="18">And it says it's been-a
three days since-a you poop.</font>

67
00:02:58,940 --> 00:03:01,640
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let me see that book.</font>

68
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:04,010
<font face="Serif" size="18">A-never.</font>

69
00:03:09,820 --> 00:03:11,790
<font face="Serif" size="18">I am not growing!
                    Look!</font>

70
00:03:11,790 --> 00:03:13,320
<font face="Serif" size="18">Nothing's happening!</font>

71
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:15,460
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, when we flew to Hawaii
     last summer,</font>

72
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:17,060
<font face="Serif" size="18">you sat on Dad's lap
      for free.</font>

73
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:18,530
<font face="Serif" size="18">I haven't grown in years.</font>

74
00:03:18,530 --> 00:03:20,690
<font face="Serif" size="18">And it's actually
        quite liberating.</font>

75
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:23,300
<font face="Serif" size="18">Gives me time to focus
      on all my other shit.</font>

76
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:25,300
<font face="Serif" size="18">B-B-But what if I
              never grow again?</font>

77
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:27,570
<font face="Serif" size="18">Look, if you really
      want to do something,</font>

78
00:03:27,570 --> 00:03:30,840
<font face="Serif" size="18">I know a doctor who specializes
      in growth treatments.</font>

79
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:33,410
<font face="Serif" size="18">A specialist --
      that's where the money is.</font>

80
00:03:33,410 --> 00:03:35,580
<font face="Serif" size="18">I should probably talk
      to my dad about this.</font>

81
00:03:35,580 --> 00:03:37,180
<font face="Serif" size="18">Steve,
              you want to talk?</font>

82
00:03:37,180 --> 00:03:39,410
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, yeah.
     I wanted to ask you --
                There's no time.</font>

83
00:03:39,420 --> 00:03:40,910
<font face="Serif" size="18">Your mother and I
               have to hurry</font>

84
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,350
<font face="Serif" size="18">down to the town
                council meeting.</font>

85
00:03:42,350 --> 00:03:43,720
<font face="Serif" size="18">I hope
              they let me speak.</font>

86
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,750
<font face="Serif" size="18">I didn't put my name on a list
  or anything.</font>

87
00:03:45,750 --> 00:03:48,360
<font face="Serif" size="18">Of course they'll let you,
 honey. You're tall.</font>

88
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:51,160
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're right.
    I'm to be taken seriously.</font>

89
00:03:52,330 --> 00:03:54,360
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, Steve,
      that really ties into</font>

90
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:56,600
<font face="Serif" size="18">what you were talking about
             earlier.</font>

91
00:03:56,600 --> 00:04:00,500
<font face="Serif" size="18">BUCKLE: The sign outside
       needs to be updated.</font>

92
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:02,770
<font face="Serif" size="18">And I say
     we just break the glass</font>

93
00:04:02,770 --> 00:04:05,710
<font face="Serif" size="18">instead of continuing
this preposterous 30-year search</font>

94
00:04:05,710 --> 00:04:07,070
<font face="Serif" size="18">for the key.</font>

95
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,710
<font face="Serif" size="18">And I say the key
 is still out there.</font>

96
00:04:08,710 --> 00:04:10,010
<font face="Serif" size="18">Agreed.</font>

97
00:04:11,850 --> 00:04:14,210
<font face="Serif" size="18">We'll now hear the last
   of the community objections</font>

98
00:04:14,220 --> 00:04:16,050
<font face="Serif" size="18">to the arena football stadium.</font>

99
00:04:16,050 --> 00:04:17,950
<font face="Serif" size="18">First up is Old Man Hansen.</font>

100
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:19,520
<font face="Serif" size="18">(clears throat)</font>

101
00:04:19,520 --> 00:04:21,920
<font face="Serif" size="18">Good people of Langley Falls,</font>

102
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:24,460
<font face="Serif" size="18">I ask you to join me</font>

103
00:04:24,460 --> 00:04:28,460
<font face="Serif" size="18">in standing up to the no-good
   crooks on our city council.</font>

104
00:04:28,460 --> 00:04:31,770
<font face="Serif" size="18">These bums are lining their
 pockets with their dirty deals,</font>

105
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:34,400
<font face="Serif" size="18">and they need to be hogtied
     and thrown down a well!</font>

106
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,970
<font face="Serif" size="18">(clears throat)</font>

107
00:04:35,970 --> 00:04:38,470
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sorry.
      I'm a little nervous.</font>

108
00:04:38,470 --> 00:04:40,140
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're doing great.</font>

109
00:04:40,140 --> 00:04:42,210
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's important
        for Langley Falls</font>

110
00:04:42,210 --> 00:04:44,810
<font face="Serif" size="18">to protect
       our historic places.</font>

111
00:04:44,810 --> 00:04:49,420
<font face="Serif" size="18">Also, while I'm up here,
  my name isn't Old Man Hansen.</font>

112
00:04:49,420 --> 00:04:52,250
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's Olmen -- Olmen Hansen.</font>

113
00:04:52,250 --> 00:04:54,550
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's Swedish. I'm 43.</font>

114
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:57,220
<font face="Serif" size="18">I think we've all heard just
about enough from Old Man H.</font>

115
00:04:57,230 --> 00:04:59,290
<font face="Serif" size="18">He doesn't know
what he's talking about.</font>

116
00:04:59,300 --> 00:05:01,160
<font face="Serif" size="18">If you don't count
 our two hockey teams</font>

117
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:03,060
<font face="Serif" size="18">and our championship
 basketball squad --</font>

118
00:05:03,070 --> 00:05:05,730
<font face="Serif" size="18">Go, Lizards -- we have no
indoor sports in this town.</font>

119
00:05:05,730 --> 00:05:09,140
<font face="Serif" size="18">We need indoor sports
for the times when it's raining!</font>

120
00:05:10,140 --> 00:05:12,570
<font face="Serif" size="18">Look at this beautiful vision
          of the future.</font>

121
00:05:12,570 --> 00:05:15,740
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's time for us to join the
 ranks of the other great cities</font>

122
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:18,150
<font face="Serif" size="18">in the Arena League
     Mid-Atlantic Conference.</font>

123
00:05:18,150 --> 00:05:21,520
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm talking Wilkes-Barre,
     Harrisburg, Wilmington.</font>

124
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:23,320
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Bleep] Wilmington!</font>

125
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:25,090
<font face="Serif" size="18">Great cities
      have to move forward.</font>

126
00:05:25,090 --> 00:05:27,190
<font face="Serif" size="18">And you know what else
       has to move forward?</font>

127
00:05:27,190 --> 00:05:28,920
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh, parades?</font>

128
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:31,960
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sharks.
         Bazooka sharks.</font>

129
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:34,530
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wow.
            Parades isn't wrong.</font>

130
00:05:34,530 --> 00:05:36,600
<font face="Serif" size="18">We can't go back to the past.</font>

131
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:40,030
<font face="Serif" size="18">We can't go back to
   a time before arena football.</font>

132
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:42,040
<font face="Serif" size="18">No go back!</font>

133
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,300
<font face="Serif" size="18">ALL:
         (chanting "No go back")</font>

134
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:45,010
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait, what is this?</font>

135
00:05:45,010 --> 00:05:46,440
<font face="Serif" size="18">COUNCILMAN #2: Oh, just some
   tree that's gonna be cut down</font>

136
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:48,110
<font face="Serif" size="18">to make way
                for the arena.</font>

137
00:05:48,110 --> 00:05:52,210
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'd like to go back on
      my previous statement.</font>

138
00:05:52,210 --> 00:05:54,820
<font face="Serif" size="18">(all gasp)
     But no go back.</font>

139
00:05:54,820 --> 00:05:56,680
<font face="Serif" size="18">This stadium cannot happen.</font>

140
00:05:56,690 --> 00:05:58,350
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mr. Smith,</font>

141
00:05:58,350 --> 00:06:00,050
<font face="Serif" size="18">you've made a passionate case
       in favor of progress,</font>

142
00:06:00,060 --> 00:06:03,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">and now, before us and God
       and the Langley charter,</font>

143
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:06,530
<font face="Serif" size="18">you mysteriously
          reverse your position?</font>

144
00:06:06,530 --> 00:06:10,900
<font face="Serif" size="18">You are, simply put, the most
electric speaker I've ever seen.</font>

145
00:06:10,900 --> 00:06:13,500
<font face="Serif" size="18">I-I just think
 we're, uh, rushing into things.</font>

146
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:15,170
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's what I'm saying.</font>

147
00:06:15,170 --> 00:06:17,540
<font face="Serif" size="18">Can someone put Grandpa to bed?
     I'm trying to talk here.</font>

148
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:19,740
<font face="Serif" size="18">We went to high school
      together!</font>

149
00:06:19,740 --> 00:06:22,680
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let's get real, you guys.
  Do we even want this stadium?</font>

150
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:25,180
<font face="Serif" size="18">Arena football
         is kind of lame.</font>

151
00:06:25,180 --> 00:06:27,010
<font face="Serif" size="18">(all gasp)
           Mr. Smith,</font>

152
00:06:27,020 --> 00:06:28,980
<font face="Serif" size="18">what is really going on here?</font>

153
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:31,990
<font face="Serif" size="18">It obviously has something to do
with that tree.</font>

154
00:06:31,990 --> 00:06:34,590
<font face="Serif" size="18">Now, come on.
           You can talk to us.</font>

155
00:06:34,590 --> 00:06:38,890
<font face="Serif" size="18">We're your town council.
        We love you.</font>

156
00:06:38,890 --> 00:06:41,360
<font face="Serif" size="18">(sighs) All right.</font>

157
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:44,770
<font face="Serif" size="18">If you must know, that tree...</font>

158
00:06:44,770 --> 00:06:46,900
<font face="Serif" size="18">that tree is my father.</font>

159
00:06:46,900 --> 00:06:49,500
<font face="Serif" size="18">What does that
                  even mean?</font>

160
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:51,670
<font face="Serif" size="18">It means he's half tree.</font>

161
00:06:51,670 --> 00:06:55,780
<font face="Serif" size="18">Question is,
      what's the other half?</font>

162
00:07:01,350 --> 00:07:03,780
<font face="Serif" size="18">(indistinct shouting)
    Order, order.</font>

163
00:07:03,790 --> 00:07:06,420
<font face="Serif" size="18">Stenographer, can you read
those last parts back?</font>

164
00:07:06,420 --> 00:07:09,120
<font face="Serif" size="18">And then Mr. Smith said,
    "That tree is my father,"</font>

165
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:11,930
<font face="Serif" size="18">at which point, the stenographer
  blacked out from excitement</font>

166
00:07:11,930 --> 00:07:13,530
<font face="Serif" size="18">and the record stops.</font>

167
00:07:13,530 --> 00:07:14,960
<font face="Serif" size="18">I apologize to the council.</font>

168
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,900
<font face="Serif" size="18">I ate some almonds.
          I'm good now.</font>

169
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:19,230
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mr. Smith, I think we're ready
      to hear what you mean</font>

170
00:07:19,230 --> 00:07:21,070
<font face="Serif" size="18">when you say
       this tree is your father.</font>

171
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:23,900
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay.
          I'll tell you.</font>

172
00:07:23,910 --> 00:07:25,240
<font face="Serif" size="18">(chairs creak)</font>

173
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:26,610
<font face="Serif" size="18">I was just a little --</font>

174
00:07:26,610 --> 00:07:27,870
<font face="Serif" size="18">(chairs creak)</font>

175
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:29,440
<font face="Serif" size="18">I was just --
        (chair creaks)</font>

176
00:07:29,450 --> 00:07:30,840
